---
title: Zesty Turkey Tacos with Guacamole
description: It's taco night with a turkey twist ! Soft flour tortillas get stuffed with ground turkey, creamy lime slaw, guacamole and a final flourish of cilantro. In a word... YUM!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-a-la-dinde-piquante-9bad68c1.jpg
